nodes.text: Jahrunba was a male Dug under Sebolto's employ during the waning years of the Galactic Republic. In 32 BBY, he was wanted for being one of three Dug brothers, the others being Nahrunba and Sahrunba, who smuggled numerous death sticks to the Gran Youth Council of Pixelito. His bounty worth 3,500 credits alive and 3,000 dead was claimed by Jango Fett.
